[size=36pt][b]IM VERY SORRY TO SAY THAT I CAN'T CONTINUE THIS CLAN MYSELF, IF ANYONE WANTS TO CONTINUE IT PLEASE PM ME AND ILL SEND THE LAYOUT FOR THE POST AND CLAN LIST TOO YOU BUT I PERSONALLY CAN'T HOST THE CLAN DUE TO REAL LIFE STUFF. SORRY ONCE AGAIN[/b].[/size]
[center][b]Intro[/b] Hi everyone, Andrew here (yet again) making a clan just for MoparScape member. It will be a clan that anyone can join (social/pk) and we will launch to choose clan cape and such once we have 30 total votes in the pole.[/center]
[center][b]How can I join?[/b] To join our clan you don't need any levels, the only requirment is that you are a member of MoparScape (don't worry your not going to get banned on the game just cause of being in this clan). Simply fill out this forum and post it in this topic. [code] Rs name: (or pm to me if you don't feel safe posting) Home world?: [/code][/center]
